{"tid":694914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇經絲打男友係你做錯野佢會第一時間篤你出黎","createTime":"2018-06-08T18:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T08:17:55.000Z","uid":186694,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d44984ddfee45e46ac18029d755c9305d625f166","tid":694914,"uid":186694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"話說男朋友屋企人係日本住，<br />\n佢公公婆婆對住自己係好節儉嘅人，<br />\n但我去日本佢地包我地住仲每一餐都堅持佢地埋單，<br />\n我地兩個後生完全冇機會孝順下佢地。<br />\n<br />\n咁我見到兩老對鞋都蝕哂但唔肯換，<br />\n就偷偷地影低佢地鞋個size同款(之前直接帶佢地入去鞋都唔肯試，唔俾我地用錢)，<br />\n再去同一間shop買然後換咗兩老對舊鞋(幫佢地收起對舊鞋唔係掉)。<br />\n<br />\n到咗夜晚去食飯，<br />\n我同男朋友行先，<br />\n係門口聽佢地咩反應。<br />\n咁公公就鐘意對新鞋嘅但婆婆就話對鞋有啲難著入去，<br />\n我男朋友就吊鬼啦，佢話叫我一早唔好送，多舊魚，叫我自己一陣同婆婆認錯。<br />\n<br />\nMeet up返個時婆婆問我地邊個咁搞野，<br />\n佢即刻篤我出黎，又成日問住係咪唔舒服，搞到我好鬼尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他例子仲有好多好多，我唔係話要佢幫我食死貓，<br />\n但唔好係佢屋企人面前指責我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe0c6196cf58cb0a90daca6124b3310419e967b","tid":694914,"uid":41960,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:38:08.000Z","msg":"飛得"},{"pid":"986cdcc24b31a439219d39ef7b9ab7464a4e8eac","tid":694914,"uid":186694,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3fe0c6196cf58cb0a90daca6124b3310419e967b","tid":694914,"uid":41960,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:38:08.000Z","msg":"飛得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:43:24.000Z","msg":"一齊咗好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5550324cebfec6f9b7745ef12b8283cd84d9e7c","tid":694914,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T19:04:53.000Z","msg":"一個連喺屋企人面前都唔肯承擔自己嘅錯<br />\n到時有起事上嚟佢只會變本加厲"},{"pid":"dc20b324f207068b29c02b450db910dec96e9a03","tid":694914,"uid":41960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"986cdcc24b31a439219d39ef7b9ab7464a4e8eac","tid":694914,"uid":186694,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3fe0c6196cf58cb0a90daca6124b3310419e967b","tid":694914,"uid":41960,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:38:08.000Z","msg":"飛得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:43:24.000Z","msg":"一齊咗好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T19:25:02.000Z","msg":"肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907cdd3099c755468cd0bba723c12f4d1960df76","tid":694914,"uid":117901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T19:27:21.000Z","msg":"似當你狗多d"},{"pid":"60e1ae35015985dbc05b94aeeefb497a220c1146","tid":694914,"uid":38648,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T19:39:44.000Z","msg":"兒登啲回覆真係得啖笑, 一啲就眼殘一啲就鳩噏<br />\n<br />\n樓主你呢個例子男友又唔係過份, 始終佢都係錫屋企兩老, 同埋睇你咁講佢本身就唔支持你咁做而你又真係做得唔好,<br />\n呢件事其實都幾小事, 你覺得佢令你難堪可以同佢傾傾<br />\n或者有冇啲真係嚴重啲嘅case?"},{"pid":"0be669e54ba5b4bf9d9c75f49c4f3d39cb403a5f","tid":694914,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T08:17:55.000Z","msg":"比佢中出完好飛啦"}]}